nta.declaration:
hybrid clock x; int attrs = -1; /* System attributes ---> code: 5 System attributes Slave---> code: 3 System attributes Unknown---> code: -1 System attributes Listening---> code: 1 System attributes Uncalibrated---> code: 2 System attributes Faulty---> code: 4 System attributes Initializing---> code: 0 */
int event = -1; /* No event ---> code: -1 Event □---> code: 0 Event Fault_detected---> code: 4 Event Master_clock_selected---> code: 3 Event Fault_cleared---> code: 5 Event Init_complete---> code: 1 Event Rs_slave---> code: 2 */
